1.11:
- Improve error messages for invalid arguments.
- Require Perl version 5.8.9 or better, because of problems with bignum in combination with Getopt::Long in
  older Perl versions.
- Minor changes to man page, usage information and INSTALL file

1.10:
- Add support for hexadecimal integers
- Add support for IPv6 addresses and IPv6 subnets
- Use Getopt::Long module to parse command line arguments
- Show error message if -i / --include-nb option is used in combination with incompatible command line arguments
- Minor changes to man page and usage information
- Add this CHANGELOG file

1.00:
- First version. Supports decimal integers, MAC addresses, IPv4 addresses and IPv4 subnets
